trans-unit.source: Provides an automated method to upgrade your shop to the latest version of PrestaShop.
trans-unit.target: Zagotavlja avtomatski način nadgradnje PrestaShop na zadnjo verzijo.

trans-unit.source: Unable to write in the directory "%s"
Back up my files and database
trans-unit.target: Naredi varnostno kopijo datotek in baze podatkov

trans-unit.source: Automatically back up your database and files in order to restore your shop if needed. This is experimental: you should still perform your own manual backup for safety.
trans-unit.target: Avtomatsko naredi varnostno kopijo datotek in baze podatkov, če boste morali povrnit podatke vaše trgovine. To je preiskusno: še vedno je priporočljivo, da ročno naredite varnostno kopijo.

trans-unit.source: To save time, you can decide not to back your images up. In any case, always make sure you did back them up manually.
trans-unit.target: Da prihranite čas, se lahko odločite, da ne naredite varnostne kopije slik. V vsakem primeru pa se prepričajte, da ste jo naredili ročno.

trans-unit.source: Unless you are using a dedicated server, select "Low".
trans-unit.target: Če ne uporabljate namenskega strežnika, izberite "nizka".

trans-unit.source: A high value can cause the upgrade to fail if your server is not powerful enough to process the upgrade tasks in a short amount of time.
trans-unit.target: Visoka vrednost lahko povzroči, da nadgradnja spodleti, če strežnik nima dovolj moči, da bi izvedel nadgradnjo v kratkem času.
Onemogoči module, ki niso od PrestaShop

trans-unit.source: As non-native modules can experience some compatibility issues, we recommend to disable them by default.
trans-unit.target: Drugi moduli lahko povzročijo težave s kompatibilnostjo, priporočamo, da jih privzeto onemogočite.

trans-unit.source: Keeping them enabled might prevent you from loading the "Modules" page properly after the upgrade.
trans-unit.target: Če jih pustite omogočene, boste morda imeli težave pri pravilnem odpiranju "Modul" strani po nadgradnji.

trans-unit.source: If you customized the default PrestaShop theme in its folder (folder name "classic" in 1.7), enabling this option will lose your modifications.
trans-unit.target: Če prilagajate privzeto PrestaShop temo v njeni mapi ( mapa z imenom "classic" v 1.7), z omogočanjem te možnosti boste izgubili spremembe.

trans-unit.source: If you are using your own theme, enabling this option will simply update the default theme files, and your own theme will be safe.
trans-unit.target: Če uporabljate svojo temo, boste z omogočanjem te možnosti samodejno posodobili datoteke privzete teme, vaša tema pa bo varna.

trans-unit.source: This will change your theme: your shop will then use the default theme of the version of PrestaShop you are upgrading to.
trans-unit.target: To bo spremenilo vašo temo: vaša trgovina bo potem uporabljala privzeto temo verzije PrestaShop na katero boste nadgradili.

trans-unit.source: This will not upgrade the default PrestaShop e-mails.
trans-unit.target: To ne bo nadgradilo privzete PrestaShom e-maile.

trans-unit.source: If you customized the default PrestaShop e-mail templates, enabling this option will keep your modifications.
trans-unit.target: Če ste spremenili privzete PrestaShop predloge mailov, bo ta možnost razveljavila vaše spremembe.
